Completely remodeled home with laminate floors throughout, new interior poplar doors, brand new kitchen with acacia countertops, new stainless steel appliances and brand new cabinets with pull out shelving. New mini split installed with AC. Bathrooms have been converted with extra large stand up showers and new vanities. The exterior features a car port, spacious and covered front porch along with a shed for additional storage. Conveniently located in a 55+ community with a clubhouse and close proximity to shops, restaurants, bus routes and more! Base Rent is $958.00 a month.

This location is a huge opportunity! Right in the heart of the Samish Way Opportunity Zone District you may be eligible for an 8-10 year tax abatement on the improvements. Great property for a 1031 Exchange. The property is currently rented, you could live in or rent out the existing house and potentially build a 4+ plex on the property, townhouses with ADU's or take the house off and build a 21 unit apartment complex (see attached). Buyer to verify all information. For more info regarding the Opportunity Zone & Urban Village Plan visit the City of Bellingham planning website.
Investor alert Almost 1/2 acre level lot in the City of Ferndale. Zoned RMH (Residential, Multi-family, High Density). Location is walking distance to downtown and is next to Vander Yacht Park.

Ready to go 48-unit site with plans and permits ready to pick up! Purchase the entire site (Lot A & Lot B for a total of 96-units) or half (Lot B, south parcel of property). Superb location ready to build near Western Washington University & all the amenities Bellingham has to offer.

Gorgeous, single story home in desirable Lynden! Spacious and bright, this home has been updated with luxury vinyl plank, stainless appliances and a newer 30 yr roof and furnace. The no-steps entry welcomes you to this thoughtfully designed, 4 bed 3.25 bath home with room to spread out. Two generous living areas, large primary bedroom with bathroom and a bonus room conversion in the garage with separate entrance and ensuite 3/4 bathroom is the perfect studio, workspace, or guest room. A true entertainer's back yard, fully fenced and complete with concrete patio, fire pit area, and loads of privacy. Fantastic Lynden neighborhood close to schools and parks!

Single Family View lot available. No Wetlands. Ready to build. Needs some trees and brush removal. Sewer and water, power, cable all in street and 100% available. Sloping lot with beautiful southern exposure of salt-water, islands and golf course. Excellent build area on lot. Topography is available. Really is ready to go!! Perfect for a custom built home, or a nice manufactured- overlooking the golf course, salt water, and sunshine. See picture for maps & building area. Tree removal and or branches- not a problem. Community amenities include; salt water boat slips, swimming pool, golf course, tennis courts, parks, private beach access and more. 85$ per month community dues. Last view lot available at this time.

This delightful south facing cottage with breathtaking ocean views is a special Point Roberts find. As you step inside, comforting features will make you feel at home right away. Sunlight delivers natural illumination. The neutral coloring of the current decor is a perfect cinema screen for your interior design vision. The crackling fireplace gives the living room a welcoming feel, creating a great spot for board games or jigsaw puzzles. The kitchen was recently updated, and is a delicious concoction of marvelous counter space and newer appliances, ready to follow your culinary directions. Go swimming directly from your doorstep, or watch the unobstructed Impressive views of the San Juan Island from the living space! Brand New Septic Tank!

Private and gated Semiahmoo Marina. Potential Catamaran Alert, Potential to buy 40 & 42 side by side. Bow in Port side tie, 44 foot slip! Semiahmoo Marina! History, majesty, mystery...what a great place to moor your boat! Semiahmoo's historic water tower stands sentinel. To the East, majestic Mt. Baker...and mystery, why are all those cars cruising Marine Drive in White Rock?! Semiahmoo Marina is only 16 nautical miles from the legendary, mystical San Juan Islands. Canada's Gulf Islands and the Inside Passage are favorite nearby destinations. Golf, tennis and swimming are available for a fee @ Semiahmoo Golf & County Club. Nice facilities, store, laundry and more.
